This paper deals with the detection of security incidents in cybersecurity environments using machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also uses the Normalized Compression Distance as a feature extraction method, which is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with text analysis and classification, which falls under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE).
